# Interactive Rating Component

A responsive **Interactive Rating Component** that allows users to select a rating from **1 to 5** and submit their feedback.

Built with **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**, focusing on **UI state management, event handling, and dynamic interface updates**.

This project is a solution to the **Interactive Rating Component challenge** from  
[Frontend Mentor](https://www.frontendmentor.io/challenges/interactive-rating-component-koxpeBUmI).

---

## Live Demo

**Live Site:**  
https://interactiveratingcomponent.vercel.app/

